SUMMARY:5-Course Gil Family Estates Winemaker Dinner at 1 Hotel Seattle
DTSTAMP:20260403T051045Z
DTSTART:20260409T010000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join the 1 Hotel Seattle team at La Loba for a special evening 
	celebrating 110 years of Gil Family Estates with a five-course tasting men
	u and curated wine pairings. Guests will enjoy wines from across the Gil f
	amily portfolio—including selections from Bodegas El Nido\, Shaya\, and Ju
	an Gil—presented by visiting winemakers and members of the Gil \n\nEach co
	urse will be introduced by Chef Oscar and his culinary team\, highlighting
	 seasonal flavors designed to complement the wines.\n\nThe evening begins 
	with a welcome toast and continues through five paired courses in our Emer
	ald Private Dining Room. Seating is communal to encourage conversation and
	 connection among fellow wine lovers.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/even
	ts/#/details/5-course-gil-family-estates-winemaker-dinner-at-1-hotel-seatt
